hadiths[64]{hadithnumber,text}:
3382,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs kisi musalman ko azad karta hai, Allah uskey eik eik uzu ke badley mein us (azad karney waley) ke eik eik uzu ko jahannam ki aag se azaad kar deta hai, yahan tak ke uski sharm-gah ko uski sharm-gah ke badley mein (azaad kar deta hai).'' muttafaq aleh."
3383,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se daryaft kiya, kon sa amal afzal hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah par eman lana aur uski raah mein jihad karna.'' wo (raawi) bayan kartey hain, maine arz kiya : kon sa ghulam azaad karna afzal hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jiski qeemat ziyada ho aur wo apney ehal ke yahan bahut pasandida ho.'' maine arz kiya, agar main aisa na kar sakoon? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' kisi bhi kaam karney waley ki madad kar, ya jo shakhs koi chiz banana nahin janta to uskey liye wo chiz bana dey.'' maine arz kya : agar main ye bhi na kar sakoon? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''logon ko apney shar se mehfooz rakh, ye aisa sadqa hai jiskey zariey to apni jaan par sadqa karta hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
3384,"Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik Erabi (dehati) (dehaati) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur usney arz kiya, mujhey koi aisa amal sikhaein jo mujhey jannat mein dakhil kar dey, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar-che tum ne baat mukhtasar ki hai lekin baat bahut aham daryaft ki hai. zi-rooh ko azad kar, aur gardan ko ghulami se azaad kar.'' usney arz kiya : kya un dono ka eik hi maana nahin? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''nahin, Itq se murad hai ke to akela usey azad karey, jabkey ''فک رقبہ''ye hai ke to uski qeemat ada karney mein muaawinat kar , ziyada doodh wala janwer bator Atiya dey aur zalim rishte-daar par meharbani aur ehsan kar, agar tum uski taqat na rakho to phir bhookey ko khana khilaoo, piyasey ko pani pilaoo, neki ka hukm karo aur burai se mana karo. agar tum uski taqat na rakho to phir khair aur bhalai ki baat ke ilawa apni zaban ko roko.'' (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan)."
3385,"Hazrat Amr bin Abasa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs masjid banata hai taake is mein Allah ka zikr kiya jaey to uskey liye jannat mein ghar bana diya jata hai, jo shakhs kisi musalman ko azaad karta hai to ye uska jahannam se fidya bin jata hai, aur jo shakhs Allah ki raah mein (ilm haasil karte hue ya jihad kartey huey) boodha ho gaya to roze-qiyamat (jab andherey hongey) uskey liye Noor hoga.'' (fi Sharahus-sunnah)."
3386,"Hazrat Ghareef bin Ayash Dailmi bayan kartey hain, ham Waasila bin Isqaa' (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaye to ham ne kaha : hamein koi aisi hadees sunaeyn jis mein koi kami beshi na ho, wo (is baat sey) naraz ho gaey aur kaha : tum Quran ki tilawat kartey ho, jabkey uska musahaf (kitab) uskey ghar mein mojud hota hai iskey bawajud wo kami beshi kar leta hai, ham ne kaha : ham ne to sirf aisi hadees ka irada kiya tha jo aapney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suni ho, unhoney kaha : ham apney eik sathi ke barey mein , jisney qatl ki wajeh se jahannam ko wajib kar liya tha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''uski taraf se ghulam azad karo, Allah uskey her uzu ke badley uskey her uzu ko jahannam ki aag se azaad kar dega.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood aur Nasai."
3387,Hazrat Samura bin Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''afzal sadqa kisi ke liye aisi sifarish karna hai jiski wajeh se kisi ki gardan azaad kar di jaey.'' (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan).
3388,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jisney ghulam mein apna hissey azaad kar diya aur uskey paas itna maal hai jo ghulam ki qeemat ko pahunchta hai, to ghulam ki munsifaana qeemat muqarrar ki jaeygi aur wo uskey shurka ko unke hisson ke mutabiq di jaeygi aur ghulam azaad ho jaeyga, warna jitna azaad ho gaya so ho gaya.'' muttafaq aleh."
3389,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jisney kisi ghulam mein mojud apna hissey azaad kar diya aur agar wo shakhs maal daar hai to ghulam ko mukammal taur par azaad kar diya jaeyga, aur agar us shakhs ke paas maal nahin to ghulam se maal kamaaney ke liye kaha jaeyga lekin is par mashaqqat nahin dali jaeygi.'' muttafaq aleh."
3390,"Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ne apni maut ke qarib apney chhe ghulam azad kar diye, aur uskey paas unke ilawa aur koi maal nahin tha, chunanche Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ghulamon ko bulaya aur unhen teen hisson mein taqseem kar diya, phir unke beech qura andazi ki to do ko azad kar diya aur chaar ko ghulam rakha, aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne iskey mutalliq sakht alfaz farmaey. unhi se marwi (bayan) Nasai ki eik riwayat mein ''iskey mutalliq sakht alfaz farmaey'' ki bajaey ye hai ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''maine irada kar liya tha ke uski Namaze janaza na padhun.'' aur Abu-Dawood ki riwayat mein hai farmaya : ''agar main uski tadfeen se pehley mojud hota to usey musalmanon ke qabristaan mein dafn na kiya jata.'' rawahu Muslim, Nasai aur Abu-Dawood."
3391,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''beta apney walid ke ehsanat ka badla sirf us surat mein ada kar sakta hai ke agar wo baap ko mamlook (ghulam) paey to usey kharid kar azad kar dey.'' rawahu Muslim."
3392,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke ansaar mein se eik aadmi ne eik ghulam mudabbir kiya (yun kaha ke meri maut ke baad ye ghulam azad hoga), aur uskey ilawa uskey paas koi aur maal nahin tha, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ye khabar pahunchi to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mujh se usey kon khareedtaa hai? ''to Naeem bin Nahaam (Raziallahu anhu) ne aath sau dirham ke badley mein usey kharid liya. aur Muslim ki riwayat mein hai ke Naeem bin Abdullah Adwi ne aath sau dirham ke iwaz usey kharid liya. aur us aadmi ne ye raqam Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein pesh ki to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne wo usey de-di, phir farmaya : ''pehley apni jaan se shuru karo aur is par sadqa karo. agar kuchh bach jaey to phir terey ghar walon ke liye , agar terey ghar walon se bach jaey to terey rishte-daaron ke liye, agar terey rishte-daaron se bach jaey to phir is tarah aur us tarah.'' raawi bayan kartey hain, apney samney aur apney daeyn, baain taqseem kar. muttafaq aleh."
3393,"Hazrat Samura ki sanad se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs qurbat daar Mohrim ka Malik ho jaey to wo (ghulam) azad hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi, Abu-Dawood aur ibne-Maja."
3394,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu), Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab aadmi ki londi uskey bachchey ko janm dey to wo uski maut ke baad azad ho jaeygi.'' rawahu Darmi."
3395,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke daur mein Umme-walad (wo londi jiskey sath uska Malik ham bistar hua aur us se aulad paida ho gaee) ki bai (saude) kiya kartey they. jab umr (Raziallahu anhu) ka daur aaya to unhoney hamein is se mana kiya to ham ruk gaey. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
3396,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs ghulam azad karey aur us (ghulam) ka maal ho to ghulam ka maal ghulam hi ka hai magar ye ke aaqa koi shart tey kar ley.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood aur ibne-Maja."
3397,"Hazrat Abu-Maleeh apney walid se riwayat kartey hain ke kisi aadmi ne ghulam mein mojud apney hissey ko azad kiya to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se uska zikr kiya gaya, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ke liye koi shareek nahin.'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey mukammal taur par azaad karney ki targheeb dilai. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
3398,"Hazrat Safina bayan kartey hain, main Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ka ghulam tha, unhoney farmaya : main tumhen azad karti hun aur tum par shart aaid karti hun ke tum zindagi bhar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat karogey, maine kaha : agar aap mujh par shart na bhi aaid karen tab bhi mein zindagi bhar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se alag na hota. unhoney mujhey azad kar diya aur mujh par shart aaid kar di. rawahu Abu-Dawood aur ibne-Maja."
3399,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib apney walid se aur wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kiya, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' makatib (wo ghulam jisne apni azaadi ka muhaida kar liya ho) par jab tak makatibat (muahide) ka eik dirham bhi baqi rehta hai to wo ghulam hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
3400,"Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tumharey kisi makatib (wo ghulam jisne apni azaadi ka muhaida kar liya ho) ke paas is qadr raqam ho ke wo ada kar sakey to wo (maalika) us se parda karey.'' rawahu Tirmizi, Abu-Dawood aur ibne-Maja."
3401,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib apney walid se aur wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ne apney ghulam se sau auqiya par makatibat (likhaai) ki, uskey zimmey sirf das auqiya ya farmaya : das Dinar baqi reh gaey aur wo unhen ada na kar saka to wo ghulam hi hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi, Abu-Dawood aur ibne-Maja."
3402,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu), Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab makatib (wo ghulam jisne apni azaadi ka muhaida kar liya ho) diyat ya meeras ka mustahiq banta hai to wo apni azaadi ke hisab se waris baneyga.'' aur Tirmizi ki riwayat mein hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' makatib ko us hissey ke mutabiq diyat di jaeygi jo usney azaadi ki diyat ada ki hai aur jo bach jaey wo diyat abd hai.'' aur Imam Tirmizi ne isey zaeef qarar diya hai. rawahu Abu-Dawood aur Tirmizi."
3403,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Abi Umra Ansari se riwayat hai ke unki walida ne ghulam azad karney ka irada kiya to unhoney usey subah tak muakhkhar (taal) kar diya, so wo faut ho gaeen, Abdur-Rehman bayan kartey hain, maine Qasim bin Muhammad se kaha : agar main unki taraf se ghulam azaad kar dun to kya unhen faeyda hoga? Qasim ne kaha : Saad bin Ubada (Raziallahu anhu), Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur unhoney arz kiya : meri walida faut ho gaeen hain, agar main unki taraf se ghulam azaad karun to kya unhen faeyda hoga? to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''haan.'' rawahu Maalik."
3404,"Hazrat Yahya bin Saeed bayan kartey hain, Abdur-Rehman bin Abi Bakr (Raziallahu anhu) haalate-neend hi mein wafat pa gaey to unki behan Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne unki taraf se bahut se ghulam azad kiye. rawahu Maalik."
3405,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jisney koi ghulam kharid us (ghulam) ke maal ki shart qaaim na ki to us (bechney waley) ke liye (uskey maal sey) kuchh bhi nahin milega.'' rawahu Darmi."
3406,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ziyada tar in alfaz ke sath qism uthaya kartey they : ''dilon ke pherney waley ki qism !'' Bukhari."
3407,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''be-shak Allah tumhen apney baap-dada ki qasmen uthaney se mana farmata hai, jisney qism uthae ho wo Allah ki qism uthaey ya phir khamosh rahey.'' muttafaq aleh."
3408,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Samura (Raziallahu anhu) riwayat kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''buton aur apney baap-dada ke namon ki qasmen mat uthaoo.'' rawahu Muslim."
3409,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu), Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jisney laat aur uzzaa (buton) ki qism uthai to usey ''لَا اِلٰہَ اِلَّا اللہُ'' padhna chahiye. aur jisney apney sathi se kaha : aao main tumharey sath jua khelon to usey sadqa karna chahiye.'' muttafaq aleh."
3410,"Hazrat Sabit bin Suhak (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jisney Islam ke ilawa kisi aur millat par jhooti qism uthai to wo wesa hi hai jaisa usney kaha, aur ibne-Adam par aisi chiz ki nazar puri karna wajib nahin jis ka wo maalik nahin, jisney kisi chiz ke sath apney aap ko duniya mein qatl kiya to roze-qiyamat usey usi ke sath azab diya jaeyga, kisi momin par lanat karna usey qatl karney ke jaisa hai jisney kisi momin shakhs par kufr ka bohtan lagaya to wo aisey hai jaisey usney usey qatl kar diya aur jisney maal badhaney ki khatir jhoota daawa kiya to Allah uski tang dasti mein izafa farmata hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
3411,"Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ki qism ! agar main kisi baat par qism utha lun aur phir uska ghair us se behtar janun to Insha-Allah main apni qism ka kaffara dunga aur us se behtar ko ikhtiyar kar lunga.'' muttafaq aleh."
3412,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Samura (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Abdur-Rehman bin Samura ! imaarat mat talab karna, agar wo tumhen tumhari talab par de-di gaee to tum uskey supurd kar diye jaaogey aur agar wo talab kiye baghair tumhen de-di gaee to is par tumhari madad ki jaeygi, aur jab tum kisi chiz par qism utha lo aur phir tum uskey ghair ko behtar jano to apni qism ka kaffara ada kar do aur jo behtar ho usey ikhtiyar kar lo.'' aur eik dusri riwayat mein hai : ''jo behtar hai usey ikhtiyar kar lo aur apni qism ka kaffara ada karo.'' muttafaq aleh."
3413,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs kisi chiz par qism uthaey aur wo us se behtar chiz jaan ley to wo apni qism ka kaffara ada karey aur jo behtar chiz hai wo karey.'' rawahu Muslim.
3414,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ki qism ! tumhara apni is qism par israr karna jo apney ghar walon ke mutalliq ho, Allah ke nazdik qism todney se ziyada gunah rakhta hai jis ka kaffara ada karna Allah ne is par farz kiya hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
3415,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tumhari qism ka wohi mafhoom moatabar hoga jis par tera sathi ( qism talab karney wala ( tumhen sacha janey .'' rawahu Muslim ."
3416,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' qism , qism talab karney waley ki niyat par moatabar hogi .'' rawahu Muslim ."
3417,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, ye aayat ''Allah tum se laghw qism ka muwaakhiza nahin kerega, us aadmi ke barey mein nazil hui jo ( aadat ke taur par) kehta hai : ''nahin, nahin ! Allah ki qism ''. ''haan, haan ! Allah ki qasam.'' Bukhari . aur Sharahus-sunnah mein masaabeh ke yehi alfaz hain aur Imam Baghwi ne farmaya : baaz muhaddeseen ne usey Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se marfoo bayan kya hai."
3418,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' apney baap dada aur apni maaon ki qasmen mat uthao aur na hi apney buton ki, aur Allah ki qism bhi sirf us surat mein uthao jab tum sachey ho.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood w Nasai ."
3419,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna : '' jisney Allah ke ilawa kisi ki qism uthai, usney shirk kya. '' rawahu Tirmizi ."
3420,"Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jisney amanat ki qism uthai to wo ham mein se nahin.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
3421,"Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs qism uthatey waqt ye kehta hai ke maamla aisa hua to main Islam se bezar w la-taalluq hun agar wo jhoota hai to wo wesa hi hai jaisa usney kaha, aur agar wo sacha hai to wo Salim taur par Islam ki taraf nahin lotega.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood w Nasai w ibne-Maja ."
3422,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) takeed ke sath qism uthatey to yun farmatey : ''us zaat ki qism jiskey haath mein abul-Qaasim ki jaan hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
3423,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) qism uthatey to yun farmatey : ''nahin! aur main Allah se maghfirat talab karta hun.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood w ibne-Maja ."
3424,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs qism uthaey aur insha Allah kahey to is par koi gunah nahin .'' Tirmizi, Abu-Dawud, Nasai, ibne-Maja , Darmi . aur Imam Tirmizi ne muhaddeseen ki eik jamaat ka zikr kya jisney usey ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) par moquf qarar diya hai. rawahu Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood w Nasai w ibne-Maja w Darmi ."
3425,"Hazrat abul-Ahwas Auf bin Malik apney walid se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha, maine arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! mujhey bataeyn ke mera chacha-zaad hai, main uskey paas jata hun aur us se koi chiz maangta hun to wo mujhey na to chiz deta hai aur na mujh se talluq jodta hai, phir usey meri zarurat padti hai to wo merey paas aata hai aur mujh se koi chiz maangta hai jabkey main qism utha chuka hun ke main usey koi chiz nahin dunga aur na us se sila rehmi karunga. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey hukm farmaya ke ''main us chiz ko ikhtiyar karun jo behtar hai aur apni qism ka kaffara ada karun.'' aur eik riwayat mein hai, raawi bayan kartey hain, maine arz kya : Allah ke Rasool ! mera chacha zaad merey paas aata hai, aur main halaf uthata hun ke main usko kuch nahin dunga aur na hi us se sila rehmi karunga . aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' apni qism ka kaffara ada karo.'' rawahu Nasai w ibne-Maja ."
3426,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) aur ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' nazar na mano kyonkey nazar taqdir ke maamle mein koi faeyda nahin deti, albatta uskey zariey bakheel se (uska maal) nikala jata hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
3427,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs Allah ki itaat ki nazar manta hai to wo usey pura karey, aur jo shakhs uski nafarmani ki nazar manta hai to wo usey pura na karey.'' Bukhari ."
3428,"Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''nafarmani ki nazar puri nahin kerni chahiye aur na us chiz ki jo insan ke bas mein nahin.'' rawahu Muslim. aur eik riwayat mein hai : ''Allah ki nafarmani mein koi nazar nahin .''"
3429,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' nazar ka kaffara qism ke kaffaarey ki tarah hai.'' rawahu Muslim ."
3430,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, us doran ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khutba irshad farma rahey they eik aadmi khada dikhai diya, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uskey mutalliq puchha to Sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya : abu-Israael hai usney nazar maana hai ke wo khada rahega, bethega nahin, wo na saye mein bethega na kalam kerega aur wo roza rakhega. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usey hukm do ke wo kalam karey, saye mein bethey aur apna roza pura karey.'' Bukhari ."
3431,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik umr-raseeda (budhey) shakhs ko dekha ke usey apney do beton ke saharey chalaya ja raha tha, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' usko kya hua ?'' unhoney bataya ke usney pedal chal kar Baitullah janey ki nazar maana hai. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah taala us se be niaz hai ke ye apni jaan ko mashaqqat mein daley .'' aur aapney usey sawar honey ka hukm farmaya. muttafaq aleh."
3432,"aur Muslim ki riwayat mein hai, Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''buzurgwar! Sawar ho jaao kyonkey Allah tum se aur tumhari nazar se be niaz hai.'' rawahu Muslim ."
3433,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Saad bin Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se us nazar ke mutalliq , jo unki walida ke zimma thi lekin wo usey pura karney se pehley wafat pa gaeen, masla puchha to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen un (ki walida) ki taraf se usey ada karney ka fatwa diya. muttafaq aleh."
3434,"Hazrat Kab bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine arz kya : Allah ke Rasool! meri tauba ka ye taqaza hai ke main apna sara maal Allah aur uskey Rasool ke liye sadqa kar dun, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''apna kuch maal rakh lo wo tumharey liye behtar hai.'' maine arz kya : main apna khaibar wala hissey rok leta hun.'' Bukhari , Muslim , aur ye eik lambi hadees ka kuch hissey hai. muttafaq aleh."
3435,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''gunah mein koi nazar nahin, aur uska kaffara qism ke kaffarey ki tarah hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood w Tirmizi w Nasai ."
3436,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jisney kisi chiz ka naam liye baghair nazar maana to uska kaffara qism ke kaffarey ki tarah hai, jisney gunah ki nazar maana to uska kaffara qism ke kaffaarey ki tarah hai, jisney kisi aisi chiz ki nazar maana jiski wo taqat nahin rakhta to uska kaffara qism ke kaffaarey ki tarah hai. aur jisney koi aisi nazar maana jiski wo taqat rakhta hai to wo usey pura karey.'' Abu-Dawud, ibne-Maja . aur baaz ne usey ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) par moquf qarar diya hai. rawahu Abu-Dawood w ibne-Maja ."
3437,"Hazrat Sabit bin Suhak (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik aadmi ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke daur mein bawaana ke maqam par oont zibeh karney ki nazar maana to wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur usney aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko (uskey mutalliq) bataya , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya wahan daure-jahiliyat ka koi but tha jiski puja ki jati ho?'' unhoney arz kiya : nahin, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya wahan unki Eidon mein se koi eid thi ?'' unhoney arz kiya, nahin, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''apni nazar puri karo kyonkey Allah ki nafarmani mein nazar puri karna zaroori nahin aur na is mein jis ka insan Malik nahin.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
3438,"Hazrat umr bin Shuaib apney walid se aur wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain ke eik aurat ne arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! maine nazar maana hai ke main aap ki mojudgi mein daf bajaun, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''apni nazar puri karo.'' aur Rizeen ne ye izafa naqal kiya, us (aurat) ne arz kiya : maine falan falan jagah jahan ehale jahiliyat zibeh kartey they, zibeh karney ki nazar maana hai to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya us jagah jahiliyat ka koi but tha jiski puja ki jati thi?'' usney arz kiya, nahin, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya us jagah unki koi eid thi?'' usney arz kiya, nahin, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''apni nazar puri karo.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood aur Razeen."
3439,"Hazrat Abu-Lubaba (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se arz kiya, meri tauba (ke itmaam mein) se hai ke main apni aabaai jagah se hijrat kar jaaun jahan maine gunah kiya tha aur main apna sara maal sadqa kar dun, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tumhari taraf se eik tihai kafi hai.'' rawahu Razeen."
3440,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Fateh Makka ke roz eik aadmi khada hua aur usney arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! maine Shan Wale Allah liye nazar maana thi ke agar Allah aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko Makka mein Fateh ata farmaai to main baitul-Maqdis mein do rakatein padhunga, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''yahin (Baitullah mein) padh lo.'' usney phir yehi baat dohrai to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''yahin padh lo.'' usney phir yehi baat dohrai to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tab teri marzi hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood aur Darmi."
3441,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) ki behan ne pedal Haj karney ki nazar maana jabkey wo uski taqat nahin rakhti thi to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah teri behan ke pedal chalney se be-niyaz hai, wo Sawar ho aur qurbani karey.'' aur Abu-Dawood ki eik riwayat mein hai : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usko hukm farmaya ke wo sawari karey aur qurbani karey. aur unhi ki eik riwayat mein hai : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah teri behan ko mashaqqat aur thakawat mein dal kar kya kerega, wo sawari karey, Haj karey aur apni qism ka kaffara ada karey.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood aur Darmi."
3442,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Maalik se riwayat hai ke Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) ne apni behan ke mutalliq Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se masla puchha ke usney nangey paaon nangey sar Haj karney ki nazar maana hai. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usey hukm do ke wo sar par kapda ley, sawari karey aur teen rozey rakhey.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood, Tirmizi, Nasai, ibne-Maja aur Darmi."
3443,"Hazrat Saeed bin Musaiyeb (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke ansaar ke do bhaiyon ke darmiyan meeras thi. un mein se eik ne apney sathi se taqseem ka mutalba kiya to usney kaha : agar tum ne dobara mujh se taqseem ka mutalba kiya to mera sara maal Kaba ke ikhrajat ke liye waqf hai. to umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne usey farmaya : Kaba ko terey maal ki zarurat nahin, apni qism ka kaffara ada kar aur apney bhai se kalam kar , kyonkey maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna hai : ''rab ki nafarmani rishte todne mein hai aur us chiz ke barey mein jis ka to Malik nahin tujh par na to koi nazar hai aur na qasam.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
3444,"Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''nazar ki do qismen hain, jo shakhs itaat mein nazar maaney to nazar Allah ke liye hai aur usey pura karna hai, aur jisney nafarmani mein nazar maana to wo shetan ke liye hai wo puri nahin karni chahiye, aur wo uska kaffara qism ke kaffare ke jaisa ada karey.'' rawahu Nasai."
3445,"Hazrat Muhammad bin Muntashir bayan kartey hain ke eik aadmi ne nazar maana ke agar Allah ne usey uskey dushman se najat di to wo apney aap ko zibeh kerega, ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se us barey mein puchha gaya to unhoney usey farmaya : Masruq se poochho , usney un se puchha to unhoney farmaya : apney aap ko zibeh na karo, kyonkey agar tum momin ho to tum ne eik momin ki jaan ko qatl kiya, aur agar tum kafir ho to tum ne aag mein janey ki jaldi ki, eik mendhaa kharido aur usey miskinon ke liye zibeh karo, kyonkey Is'haq (Alaihissalam) tum se behtar they aur unke fidya main eik mendhaa diya gaya, jab ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ko bataya gaya to unhoney farmaya : main bhi tumhen isi tarah ka fatwa deney ka irada rakhta tha. rawahu Razeen."
